General.Name: Shaver Shop Group Ltd
General.Description: Shaver Shop Group Limited engages in the retailing of personal care and grooming products in Australia and New Zealand. It offers electric shavers, beard trimmers, hair clippers, body groomers, head shavers, manual shavers, oral care, massage and wellness, and skincare and haircare products for men; and hair removal, hair styling, beauty, oral care, massage and exercise, and fragrance products for women. It offers its products through its corporate owned stores, as well as online through its websites and online marketplaces. The company was formerly known as Lavomer Riah Holdings Pty Ltd and changed its name to Shaver Shop Group Limited in May 2016. Shaver Shop Group Limited was founded in 1986 and is based in Chadstone, Australia.
